name: プロデューサー
text: お疲れ、なんだかいい顔してるな
trans:
Great job out there! 
You seem really happy right now.

name: 甘奈
text:
えへ、今回はかなりいい感じだったかな！
いつもみたいに上手くダンスできたと思うんだ☆
trans:
Ehe, it's because I did pretty well today! 
I think I was able to properly execute the dance 
steps just like how I usually do☆

name: 甘奈
text: プロデューサーさんから見て、どーだった？
trans:
Though, how did it look from your view, 
Producer-san?

name: プロデューサー
text: ああ、明るい甘奈のいいところが出てたな
trans:
Well, from my view, I could see your bright and 
cheerful side perfectly, Amana.

name: 甘奈
text: えへへ、だったら良かったかな☆
trans:
Ehehe, if that's the case, then I guess I did pretty
well☆

name: 甘奈
text:
番組に出ると
学ぶことがたくさんあるね！
trans:
When it comes to appearing on television, I guess the
highlight is all the learning you get along the way!

name: プロデューサー
text: じゃあ、その学んだところを次に生かそう！
trans:
If that's the case, let's put our learnings into action
the next time we get the chance!

name: 甘奈
text:
うんっ！　それで番組を盛り上げて、
見てくれた人にいっぱい楽しんでもらうんだ☆
trans:
Yeah! If we do that, the broadcast will get super
fired up, and even more people will tune in and enjoy☆
